---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout title='Welcome to Astro.'>
  <main>
    <video autoplay muted loop id='myVideo' class='absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-screen object-cover z-0'
           poster='/img.webp'>
      <source src='/RedWoman_compressed.mp4' type='video/mp4' />
    </video>
    <section id='hero' class='flex flex-col justify-between items-start'>
      <nav class='flex flex-row justify-between w-full items-center px-5 py-4 z-50'>
        <h1 class='text-white md:text-[44x] text-[28px] leading-[48px] font-medium'>CLAN™</h1>
        <a
          class='bg-white rounded-[50px] md:h-11 h-7 px-4 md:text-xl text-base flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-950'>
          Sign In
        </a>
      </nav>
      <div class='flex flex-col md:justify-end justify-between h-full p-5 z-50'>
        <h3 class='md:text-[88px] text-[48px] leading-tight text-white'>
          growth agency for fashion brands and independent designers
        </h3>
        <div class='flex flex-col md:grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-8'>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            10X avg. revenue growth <span class='text-dusty-rose'>of connected brands in the first year of work</span>
          </p>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            100× less spending <span class='text-dusty-rose'>on marketing, website, analytics, compared to other ways of building</span>
          </p>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            5+ saved years<span class='text-dusty-rose'> of saved time on growth and experiment</span>
          </p>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            30%<span class='text-dusty-rose'> less spending on operational management</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='bg-white sm:min-h-screen sm:pt-28 pt-10 px-5'>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>We help brands make their first money, develop
        strategy, and take the next steps in their journey, significantly increasing revenue and growth rate. <span
          class='text-neutral-300'>We do this through our extensive business savvy, experience in fashion, and understanding of the market. </span>
      </p>
      <div class='flex flex-col md:grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 w-full mt-8 h-[796px]'>
        <div class='relative'>
          <img src='/img_8.png' class='md:h-full' alt='img_8' />
          <p class='absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[220px] text-[20px] leading-[24px]'>
            Omut Jewelry
            <span class='text-gray'>boosted revenue tenfold in one year after five years of working in debt</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='grid grid-rows-2 gap-4'>
          <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4'>
            <div class='relative'>
              <img src='/img_9.png' class='h-full' alt='img_9' />
              <p class='absolute top-[47%] left-0 w-[220px] text-[20px] leading-[24px]'>
                Vereja
                <span class='text-gray'>doubled its sales after rearranging its product assortment</span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class='relative'>
              <img src='/img_10.png' class='h-full' alt='img_10' />
              <p class='absolute top-0 right-0 w-[220px] text-[20px] leading-[24px]'>
                Mirstores
                <span class='text-gray'>discovered the break-even point and established financial management</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class='relative'>
              <img src='/img_11.png' class='h-full' alt='img_11' />
              <p class='absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[220px] text-[20px] leading-[24px]'>
                Beaded Breakfast
                <span class='text-gray'>tripled sales after rebranding and its first marketing campaign</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='bg-white sm:min-h-screen sm:pt-28 pt-10 px-5'>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>We work with the entire brand itself, analyzing
        financials, business, production, market, and developing a strategy to execute. <span
          class='text-neutral-300'>Mostly, we are starting with online sales, gradually moving towards bigger and more complex tasks. In our ideal world, you handle design and production while we take care of everything else.</span>
      </p>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 w-full mt-8 h-[390px]'>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <Icon name='box' class='w-6 h-6' />
          <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Advertising & branding
          </p>
          <p class='text-gray text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Mostly we are starting with online sales, website, and simple financial model.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <Icon name='triangle' class='w-6 h-6' />
          <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Financial management
          </p>
          <p class='text-gray text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            In the first months, we are developing a simple financial model which allows us to manage budgets, and
            understand the most profitable products. Then we are developing a more complex model, that optimise
            production, sales, and allows us to plan growth years ahead.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <Icon name='shape' class='w-6 h-6' />
          <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Marketing and engineering
          </p>
          <p class='text-gray text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            We design and develop websites and crm platforms
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <Icon name='dots' class='w-6 h-6' />
          <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Assortment management
          </p>
          <p class='text-gray text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Understanding most valuable and sellable products, we are developing assortment. Sometimes it includes
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class='bg-white sm:min-h-screen sm:pt-28 pt-10 px-5'>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>
        We charge income commissions and work as an outsourced team, developing partnership relationships.
        <span class='text-neutral-300'>
          Firstly, this is the only way for most brands to afford our services. Secondly, we put our skin in the game: if our work is ineffective, you are not risking anything; if it's effective, we make money together. Simple.
        </span>
      </p>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 w-full mt-8 h-[390px]'>
        <div class='flex flex-col bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px] justify-between'>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-3'>
            <Icon name='circle' class='w-6 h-6' />
            <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight max-w-md'>
              If you want to test everything out. We’ll take over marketing and sales, quickly increasing your income in
              first months or even weeks. That will help us to build a strategy and financial model.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-neutral-950 text-2xl font-medium leading-tight'>
              15% for marketing
            </p>
            <p class='text-gray text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
              no risks for start
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px] justify-between'>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-3'>
            <Icon name='circle2' class='w-6 h-6' />
            <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight max-w-md'>
              When you are ready to build, we’ll take responsibility for the strategy execution, working on every aspect
              of the brand, marketing, and production. It will gave you significant growth in 6-12 months.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-neutral-950 text-2xl font-medium leading-tight'>
              30% for direction and growth
            </p>
            <p class='text-gray text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
              best for long-term and significant results
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='bg-white sm:pt-28 pt-10 px-5'>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>We stand against old-fashioned ways imposed by the
        community and simply making money. Independently, quickly, free of prejudices.<span
          class='text-neutral-300'>
        If you have a good product, a little bit of sales, and share our vision, we are ready to go. We work with jewelry, shoes, perfumes, accessories, clothing, and furniture.</span>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class='p-5 bg-white h-screen relative'>
      <video autoplay muted loop id='another' class='w-full h-full object-cover z-0 rounded-[20px]'
             poster='/img.webp'>
        <source src='/rage_longer_compressed.mp4' type='video/mp4' />
      </video>
      <div
        class='flex flex-col items-center absolute transform -translate-y-1/2 top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-50 w-full'>
        <p class='text-white md:text-[88px] text-[48px] leading-tight text-center md:max-w-4xl'>
          rage, rage against the dying of the light
        </p>
        <div class='flex flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 text-white mt-24'>
          <a>x.com</a>
          <a>pm.me</a>
          <a>t.me</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

